btor&rsquo;s personal property&rdquo; is not sufficient. UCC &sect; 9-108, inc. cmt. 2.  If I am not following your concern, please clarify.  Steve    Nick Wolfe @ 2022-07-13 10:28:09 wrote:  There is an error in this essay. The prompt states that the secured party used a super generic description in the financing statement(which is acceptable) but then the sample answer states that the super generic description of collateral is not acceptable in a security agreement, which is the what the facts state."	"Dena Ray (Ed)"
